    "body": "I do not know enough about sync modes in nethermind/open-ethereum but we should be able to support any node that is able to do the equivalent of `fast-sync` in those clients. \r\n\r\nWe won't be able to support any `light sync` nodes from geth/nethermind/open-ethereum. But the default sync modes used should be fine. \r\n\r\nAlthough the obvious caveat is that you need a fully synced eth1 node before anything can be done. ",
